tweet: “I was literally in tears how he [President Zelenskyy] heroically chose to defend the country of Ukraine.”  These are the parents of one of my staffers. We #StandWithUkraine and are inspired by their work to share their story to aid Ukrainian refugees!

name: Treasurer Ball
tweet: Exciting new saving measures have been made for Kentuckians with Disabilities through STABLE Kentucky accounts just in time for #DevelopmentalDisabilitiesAwarenessMonth. You can now save $16,000 + $12,880 (if employed) in one year through STABLE KY! $28,880 annual savings!
